Subject: [PATCH 04/11] qla4xxx: Quiesce driver activities while loopback
Git-repo: git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/jejb/scsi.git
Git-commit: 026fbd3aaae796d2457898497374b68f3477ee2f
Patch-mainline: Queued in subsystem maintainer repo
References: BZ#802095, FATE#313902

Quiesce all different activities performed by driver upon the link events
while loopback diagnostics is in progress.

